<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="principle-n">principle <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'prɪnsəpl/    美 /'prɪnsəpl/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>原理；原则</strong></h4>
<p>the basic idea that a plan or system is based on：</p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>the <strong>basic principle</strong>
基本原理/基本原则</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Excellent customer service should be our <strong>guiding principle</strong>. 
优秀的客户服务应该成为我们的指导原则。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>道德准则；行为准则</strong></h4>
<p>a moral rule or belief about what is right and wrong, that influences how you behave：</p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a <strong>man of principle</strong>
有原则的人</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I refuse to lie about it; <strong>it’s against my principles</strong>. 
我绝不为此事撒谎，那有悖我的原则。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>She’d never ask to borrow money, <strong>on principle</strong>. 
原则上，她从不向别人借钱。</p></div>

<h4 id="3">3.★ <strong>(机器等的) 工作原理；(自然界的) 定律；法则</strong></h4>
<p>a general or scientific law that explains how sth works or why sth happens：</p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Archimedes’ principle 
阿基米德定律</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>These machines both work on the same principle. 
这两台机器的工作原理是相同的。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="in-principle">in principle</h3>
<p>1.★ <strong>理论上；原则上：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I agree with it in principle but I doubt if it will happen in practice. 
理论上我同意，但是不知道实际上能否可行。</p></div>

<p>2.★ <strong>大体上；基本上：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>We agree with it in principle but we still need to discuss the details.
我们大体上同意，但是仍需讨论细节。</p></div>

<h2 id="_3">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>Anyway, I can’t cheat him — it’s against all my <strong><em>_</em></strong>_ (原则).   （2011 浙江改）  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. principles  </p></div>